title: etnies Under Our Feet: Tyler Bledsoe
description:
etni.es/under-our-feet-tb
Lookout below! Check the view Under Our Feet and name the tricks each week to win! We'll post a new edit every Monday and announce a winner every Friday! This week's featured pro is Tyler Bledsoe and his prize pack includes the GoPro HD HERO2 Camera, waterproof housing & assorted mounting hardware, limited edition Tyler Bledsoe Alien Workshop deck and a pair of the new etnies RCT. One person will win it all!
Step 1. Watch Tyler’s edit here.
Step 2. Name each trick in his line.
Step 3. LIKE etnies on Facebook.
Step 4. Submit your entry form at etni.es/under-our-feet-tb and
Step 5. Check the etnies Facebook on Friday when we'll announce the winner!
Good luck... This one’s a doozy.
